---
---

<section id="about" class="py-24 px-6">
	<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
		<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">
			About<span class="text-[var(--color-accent)]">.</span>
		</h2>
		<div class="w-12 h-1 bg-[var(--color-accent)] rounded mb-10"></div>

		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
			<div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-5 text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
				<p>
					My professional journey began outside software development, where I spent several years working in the 3D animation industry. That experience taught me how to collaborate in multidisciplinary teams, solve complex problems, and adapt quickly to new challenges.
				</p>

				<p>
					After completing my training in web development and software engineering, I'm now building my career as a software developer. I've developed projects across both frontend and backend, and I enjoy understanding how every part of an application works—from the user interface to the underlying architecture.
				</p>

				<p>
					I'm naturally curious and always looking to learn something new. Rather than limiting myself to a single area, I'm excited to explore different fields of software development, contribute to meaningful projects, and continue growing as an engineer.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="space-y-4">
				<div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-surface)] border border-[var(--color-border)]">
					<p class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Location</p>
					<p class="text-white text-sm">Spain</p>
				</div>

				<div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-surface)] border border-[var(--color-border)]">
					<p class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Focus</p>
					<p class="text-white text-sm">Software Development</p>
				</div>

				<div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-surface)] border border-[var(--color-border)]">
					<p class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Interests</p>
					<p class="text-white text-sm">Open Source, AI, Linux</p>
				</div>

				<div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-surface)] border border-[var(--color-border)]">
					<p class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Current Goal</p>
					<p class="text-white text-sm">Growing as a Software Engineer</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
